OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1778425867
OL,3,CBirmingham city council leader John
OL,4,CCotton accepts defeat for Labour
OL,6,FThe Labour leader of Birmingham City
OL,7,FCouncil John Cotton has accepted
OL,8,Fdefeat for his party as the Labour
OL,9,Fvote in the city collapses.
OL,11,FThe results so far in the city have
OL,12,Fbeen fractured across political
OL,13,Fparties and the Independents.
OL,15,F"We always knew this was going to be a
OL,16,Ftough election."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
