PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1778425867
OL,3,CBirmingham city council leader John
OL,4,CCotton accepts defeat for Labour
OL,6,FAlthough it's not been officially
OL,7,Fannounced, he accepts he has lost his
OL,8,Fown seat, and told ITV Central
OL,9,Fpolitical reporter Lewis Warner that
OL,10,Falthough it's been a disappointing day
OL,11,Ffor Labour, it was also expected.
OL,13,FHe rejected blaming the Prime Minister
OL,14,Finsisting that "issues go beyond one
OL,15,Findividual".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
