PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1778425867
OL,3,CBirmingham city council leader John
OL,4,CCotton accepts defeat for Labour
OL,6,FCotton lost his seat after serving as
OL,7,Fleader of the council for three years
OL,8,Fbut said he's proud of being able to
OL,9,Fsort out some of the "internal issues
OL,10,Faround management and finances around
OL,11,Fequal pay".
OL,13,FDespite the challenges he said "it's
OL,14,Fbeen an immense privilege serving as
OL,15,Fcouncillor for quarter of century."
OL,17,FBin strikes
OL,19,FHe urged the next leader to press
OL,20,Fforward with his bin strike deal.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
